	"companion_Farm_Spring_Spouse": "You seem to be doing a great job with how you're planning for the year of farming, my love.#$b#I'm proud of you.$h",
	"companion_Farm_Summer_Spouse": "%Jio wiped a rolling sweat from your face.#$b#Don't push yourself too hard, my love.#$b#Let me lighten the load whenever you need it to be.$h",
